{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T15:02:33.792Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Executing the tool"},{"type":"text","text":" is the step where "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"your application runs Claude's requested function"},{"type":"text","text":" after receiving a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_use"},{"type":"text","text":" block. This is where Claude stops generating text and your code performs the actual action — database query, API call, file read, or code execution."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Critical distinction"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Claude doesn't execute the tool — your code does. Claude responds with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"stop_reason: 'tool_use'"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_use"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks, your code executes the operation, and you send back a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"tool_result"},{"type":"text","text":".\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why It Matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Without execution"},{"type":"text","text":": Claude just says \"I need to check stock price\" → no actual data fetched"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"With execution"},{"type":"text","text":": Your code calls "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"getStockPrice(\"AAPL\")"},{"type":"text","text":" → returns 175.43 → Claude incorporates result → \"AAPL is $175.43\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"For your distributed system